Coding and scripting are two of the most important skills for anyone working in DevOps. Without these skills, you'll be unable to automate tasks or work with code repositories
evolving and improving products at a faster pace than organizations using traditional software development and infrastructure management processes.
Coding and scripting are two important skillset that DevOps engineer should possess. Python, Ruby, Python, Java, Javascript, PHP, Bash, Shell and Node. js are among the most recommended programming/scripting languages. Linux is one of the operating environments that hardcore developers continue to use even to this day.

